{
  "stem": "3002.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because where he left his family, on the Russian-Polish border, the Russians were there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was the part which was taken by the Russian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I think they made a deal, Stalin and, and Hitler, that this part belongs to Russia, where he left his parents.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They lived there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he organized this truck full of people to go, to make their way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody knew how.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But made their way toward the east, towards the Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that was a terrible experience because everybody wanted to get into this truck.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was so packed, terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A needle couldn't have a place there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finally, he had gasoline enough to go a little while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At one point, my brother got out from the truck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said he has to take a break and breathe some fresh air because it was so sticky.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the meantime, shootings was from all sides.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He got lost.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were screaming after him, calling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We couldn't find him anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this truck, after a while, lost gasoline, couldn't-- didn't have any more, couldn't go any further.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we decided to come back to Przedborz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In the meantime, the Germans already settled in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the beginning, we still could travel a little.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was, there was, those were the first days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was eager to go back to Konskie, to my parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you ever see your brother again?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later on.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was eager to see my parents in Konskie.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when I made my way--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything was-- made my way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By bus.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, we didn't still have any yellow stars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- the Germans weren't organized, just for the first two, three days, when they came in.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
